 panel","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\APP\\APP-Windows","areaShort":"APP / APP-Windows","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2025-01-08","description":"\u003cdiv>Email is filing after closing task panel \u003c/div>","functionality":"Tasks / Task Manager","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/809901","tests":[]},{"id":809987,"title":"After deleting the file, displaying as duplicate file","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\APP\\APP-Windows","areaShort":"APP / APP-Windows","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2025-01-08","description":"\u003cdiv>This is an issue reported as part of our email/document filing process.&nbsp; \u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cb>\u003cu>Steps:\u003cbr>\u003c/u>\u003c/b>\u003cspan>\u003cp>\u003col>\u003cli>From Outlook, user uploads an email/attachment to an empty/new folder \u003c/li>\u003cli>A few minutes later, the user doesn't want to keep the file anymore and thus deletes it on the Files module of HighQ collaborate instance \u003c/li>\u003cli>Now, the folder is empty again \u003c/li>\u003cli>Now, user tries again to save the same email/attachment from Outlook to HighQ collaborate (same folder) and gets a deduplication message. \u003c/li> \u003c/ol> \u003c/p>\u003c/span>","functionality":"Files / Documents","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/809987","tests":[]},{"id":810705,"title":"IMA App: Taskpane - AI Extract information button click","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\APP\\APP-Windows","areaShort":"APP / APP-Windows","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2025-01-13","description":"\u003cdiv> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cimg src=\"https://tr-legal.visualstudio.com/66e74794-9916-410b-b624-07d49748bbff/_apis/wit/attachments/711c317c-9ab3-4faa-85a2-a24a0a567b68?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Mobile / App","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/810705","tests":[]},{"id":811999