-16&quot; after choosing a date, and it's &quot;17 Jan 2025&quot; when the field is blurred (un-focused).&nbsp; \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cimg src=\"https://tr-legal.visualstudio.com/66e74794-9916-410b-b624-07d49748bbff/_apis/wit/attachments/b617e829-b4df-44cb-b0cd-475596757403?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image style=\"width:296px;height:267px;\" width=296 height=267>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cimg src=\"https://tr-legal.visualstudio.com/66e74794-9916-410b-b624-07d49748bbff/_apis/wit/attachments/651af89c-8b87-44a5-9f13-dfb0a14e6459?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image style=\"width:267px;height:154px;\" width=267 height=154>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Other","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/812474","tests":[]},{"id":812622,"title":"[Customer Issue Investigation] Favorites Not loading","state":"Blocked","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\APP\\APP-Windows","areaShort":"APP / APP-Windows","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2025-01-23","description":"\u003cdiv>\u003cb>User:&nbsp;\u003c/b>beejal.patel@diageo.com&nbsp;\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cb>Instance:\u003c/b>&nbsp;\u003cspan style=\"color:rgb(28, 43, 52);font-family:NotoSans, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Lucida Sans Unicode&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:13px;text-align:left;background-color:rgb(212, 236, 249);display:inline !important;\">\u003ca href=\"http://www.pathfinderdiageo.com\">www.pathfinderdiageo.com\u003c/a>\u003cbr>\u003c/span>\u003cdiv>\u003cb>Number of Impacted Users: \u003c/b>1, only her, it's working for her colleague.\u003cbr>\u003cb>Occurrence:\u003c/b> Permanent Issue\u003cbr>\u003cbr>\u003cb>\u003cu>Description of the issue:&nbsp;\u003c/u>\u003c/b>\u003cbr>User can't get the favorite list of folder loaded properly when trying to save emails and attachments. She can mark folders as &quot;favorite&quot; both on Outlook and HighQ sides, however, the folders never appear in the Favorite folder list. Only one, old folder, is gett