","tests":[]},{"id":740197,"title":"Isheet column conditionality not working when isheet item is created with Display as Form using Site Navigation.","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\COL\\COL-Isheet\\iSheet-KTLO","areaShort":"COL / COL-Isheet / iSheet-KTLO","issueSource":"Scrum QA","createdDate":"2024-02-19","description":"\u003cdiv>Isheet column conditionality not working when isheet item is created with Display as Form using Site Navigation.\u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"iSheet","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/740197","tests":[]},{"id":751790,"title":"crcityattorney : Griffin_sheet_initiateContractItemProcessing sp is taking more than 1 hour","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\COL\\COL-Isheet\\iSheet-KTLO","areaShort":"COL / COL-Isheet / iSheet-KTLO","issueSource":"Monitoring","createdDate":"2024-05-03","description":"\u003cdiv>\u003cb>Issue :\u003c/b>&nbsp;Griffin_sheet_initiateContractItemProcessing sp is taking more than 1 hour \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cb>Investigation Summary :&nbsp;\u003c/b> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cb>\u003cbr>\u003c/b> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>We have investigated the logs and found that&nbsp;Griffin_sheet_initiateContractItemProcessing sp is taking more than 1 hour . \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cimg src=\"https://tr-legal.visualstudio.com/66e74794-9916-410b-b624-07d49748bbff/_apis/wit/attachments/ccdbd3dc-24b5-4885-ac2b-6a0ba14a2747?fileName=image.png\" alt=Image>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003ca href=\"https://tr-highq-prod.datadoghq.com/logs?query=crcityattorney%20source:collaborate_sp_threshold%20Griffin_sheet_initiateContractItemProcessing%20&amp;agg_m=count&amp;agg_m_source=base&amp;agg_q=status%2cservice&amp;agg_q_source=base%2cbase&amp;agg_t=count&amp;cols=host%2cservice%2c%40Database.Connection.AT&amp;event=AgAAAY84iDbMlmxEGQAAAAAAAAAYAAAAAEFZODRpRUwwQUFEWWNERnBsRDA5OUFCUgAAACQAAAAAMDE4ZjM4OTEtYWFjZS00NjYzLWE3NzUtMDc0M