adata iSheet grids, exhausting the configured heap (e.g. ~4 GB observed in logs) \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cspan>Expected behavior\u003cbr>\u003c/span>\u003cdiv>Task list / scroll actions complete within normal time and memory bounds.\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>Database reads are bounded (pagination, limits, or streaming) so heap usage stays stable.\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cspan>&nbsp;\u003c/span> \u003c/div>\u003cspan>\u003c/span>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Tasks / Task Manager","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/914939","tests":[]},{"id":914942,"title":"On dashboards page, delete message should be display properly as per page type.","state":"Approved","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\Core\\HQ-Core-SQ1","areaShort":"Core / HQ-Core-SQ1","issueSource":"Scrum QA","createdDate":"2026-03-24","description":"\u003cdiv>On dashboards page, delete message should be display properly as per page type.\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Other","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/914942","tests":[{"id":914537,"title":"Verify delete operation for Dashboard Pages (Legacy and Moernised page)","automationStatus":"TBD"}]},{"id":916051,"title":"deloittelegal -p1-d9a-zuk1 - continuously consuming high memory mainly while Griffin_task_getAllTasks_groupByList SP execution","state":"Approved","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\Core\\HQ-Core-SQ1","areaShort":"Core / HQ-Core-SQ1","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2026-03-27","description":"\u003cdiv>\u003cspan>\u003c/span> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">p1-d9a-zuk1 - continuously consuming high memory mainly due to&nbsp;\u003ca href=\"https://portal.deloittelegal.com/\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(0, 90, 158);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer;\">deloittelegal\u003c/a>. And it is causing slowness and connectivity issues on the DB, We have received about 20 alerts so far due to thi