ing, automated workflows, or version tracking. \u003c/p>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Upload","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/829381","tests":[]},{"id":840102,"title":"Siteadmin user is not able to create iSheet from Excel file","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\HQ-Modernization-SQ1","areaShort":"HQ-Modernization-SQ1","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2025-05-22","description":"\u003cdiv>Siteadmin user is not able to create iSheet from Excel file (iSheet with 50 columns and 500 records)\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>Test case ID 233745. Test is automated \u003c/div>","functionality":"iSheet","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/840102","tests":[]},{"id":843216,"title":"iSheet modernization : Clicking on show more link of multi line column data throws system error for TMD isheet in case of wijmo false","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\HQ-Modernization-SQ1","areaShort":"HQ-Modernization-SQ1","issueSource":"Scrum QA","createdDate":"2025-06-03","description":"\u003cdiv>Test Environment : \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr>Precondition :&nbsp; \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>Wijmo should be off from ASP and System admin. \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>One TMD isheet should be created with &quot;Set character limit to truncate multiple line text&quot; property checked. \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>One multi line column should be added. \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>One task should be added and multi line column data. (Add multiple line data so that show more link will be display) \u003c/div>","functionality":"iSheet","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/843216","tests":[]},{"id":848425,"title":"SchedulingService MS->Payload Field  Not Inserted When Exceeding 256 Characters","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\HQ-Modernization-SQ1","areaShort":"HQ-Modernization-SQ1","issueSource":"Internal","createdDate":"2025-06-17","description":"\u003cdiv>The payload column in t