taData.modulePage=dSearch\">supportuatvfour\u003c/a> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>After discussion with the SWAT team, I have raised this bug ticket. \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>Let me know if anything is required to investigate this issue further. \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>Thanks. \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Search / Indexing","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/916282","tests":[]},{"id":916304,"title":"Getting a \"Leave site\" message when uploading documents in bulk","state":"Active","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\SWAT","areaShort":"SWAT","issueSource":"Production","createdDate":"2026-03-30","description":"\u003cdiv>\u003cb>Customer Name: \u003c/b>Debevoise\u003cspan>\u003cspan dir=ltr>\u003cbr>\u003c/span>\u003c/span> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv> \u003c/div>\u003cdiv>\u003cbr> \u003c/div>\u003cspan>\u003cspan dir=ltr>\u003cbr>\u003c/span>\u003c/span>\u003cb>Client’s initial description copied from Support ticket:&nbsp;\u003c/b>\u003cdiv>\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">We are having more issues with HighQ today with uploading new folder structures and files to the Files module.\u003c/span>\u003cp style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-size:medium;\">\u003cspan style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;\">There are a total of 297 files we are moving of varying size (typically 0.5mb – 5mb approx in size) within a new folder structure to one of our client sites, but we are receiving constant errors as below:\u003c/span> \u003c/p>\u003cp style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;font-size:medium;\">\u003cspan style=\"font-family:Calibri, sans-serif;font-size:11pt;\">Firstly this dialogue box will pop up, when we click cancel it will fail to upload a sequence of files, before restarting, but then the message will pop up again:\u003c/span> \u003c/p>\u003cdiv>\u003cimg src=\"https://tr-legal.visualstudio.com/66e74794-9916-410b-b624-07d49748b