perations &amp; Technology)\u003c/a> \u003c/div>","functionality":"iSheet","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/917452","tests":[]},{"id":831110,"title":"After restarting AKS POD _advanceai , Uptime is not reflecting properly.","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\TSI-Technical Support Investigation","areaShort":"TSI-Technical Support Investigation","issueSource":"Automation","createdDate":"2025-04-21","description":"\u003cdiv>After restarting AKS POD -advanceai . Uptime is not reflecting properly. \u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"AI / CoCounsel","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/831110","tests":[]},{"id":892587,"title":"UI/UX: Logo missing in emails generated prior to saffron email update.","state":"New","areaPath":"HighQ Tech\\UID","areaShort":"UID","issueSource":"Scrum QA","createdDate":"2025-12-02","description":"\u003cdiv>Logo missing in emails generated prior to saffron email update.\u003cbr> \u003c/div>","functionality":"Other","url":"https://dev.azure.com/tr-legal/HighQ%20Tech/_workitems/edit/892587","tests":[]}]</script>

